The resolution of the Foreign Affairs Committee “is awe of the people of Libya for their extraordinary courage and perseverance in the pursuit of freedom” and thanks the men and women of the United States Armed Forces and their coalition partners who have been involved in the military operation to defend the Libyan people for their extraordinary courage and professionalism.
